sentences.en: As they're handmade, each one varies slightly.
sentences.cn: 由于它们是手工制作的，彼此都会有些微小的差异。

sentences.en: Connie Corleone presented the baby with a silk layette handmade in Italy, enormously expensive and beautiful.
sentences.cn: 康妮-考利昂给她送了一套婴儿用品,丝绸衣服、被褥等都是意大利手工制品, 非常昂贵,非常漂亮.

sentences.en: Handmade Acrylic Products, Photo Frames, Pharmaceutical Gifts, Paper Weight, Award, Card Holder.

sentences.en: Handmade goods appeal to those who are tired of cookie-cutter products.
sentences.cn: 手工制品受到那些已厌倦划一产品的人的欢迎。

sentences.en: He builds handmade classical and flamenco guitars using traditional methods of construction.
sentences.cn: [他用传统工艺制作手工古典吉他和弗拉明戈吉他. ]

sentences.en: It's an eye made of glass. Handmade in Turkey.
sentences.cn: 是玻璃做的一颗眼睛.土耳其的手工制品.

sentences.en: It's handmade and the inlaid designs are etched in.

sentences.en: Nearly all clothing was handmade from the fibers of plants or from the hides of animals.

sentences.en: The beads they use are handmade in the Jura mountains in central France.

sentences.en: The handmade outsole is heavily stitched with thin needles.
sentences.cn: 鞋底手工纳制而成,针眼细密.

sentences.en: The nightdress has handmade lace round the armholes and neckline.
sentences.cn: 这件女式睡衣的袖孔和领口都镶着一圈手织花边。

sentences.en: There are various desktop items made in tree - free handmade paper.
sentences.cn: 我们有各式各样的桌上用品,均是采用无树手工纸制作.

sentences.en: Yes, China has some good luthiers making handmade concert quality guitars.
sentences.cn: 是的, 中国现在有很多好琴师在制作手工演奏会琴.
